The world has recognised the significance of Sanskrit in various spiritual and technological aspects of human life. Sanskrit also has a tremendous importance in the Indian rituals of diversified cultures.

*Persona Fest* is amongst the most awaited techno cultural event being organized by the MIT-ADT University. More than 11,000 Students from the 125+ Institutions and Universities participate in this MIT-ADT University Flagship event. Students from the various colleges under the MIT-ADT University as well as the students from the prestigious Institutions and Universities have been participating in the wide ranging events.
Following are the amazing technical  sub-events to be held in Persona 2023:-
2) *Codebreak 4.0*: national level hackathon organized for all inter-disciplinary students.
*3) Design Competition-UI Thon* Design competition with Design Steps, Paper Wireframing, Low-Fidelity Prototyping, and High-Fidelity Prototyping.
*4) Project Expo:* Students get a platform to showcase their projects they have build and compete with the other students projects in different domains.
*5) Brains On Fire:* Participants will be required to identify an issue and present relating to the domain by brain storming.
6) *Idea Expo* -All the students (Insiders) get a platform to showcase their ideas they have build and compete with the other students ideas
7) *Poster Competition* - Poster competition on Role of Science in the developement of Art, Design and Technology
8) *Techno Escape Room*- The objective is to solve a mission and escape using the elements of the room before the time runs out. Tentatively decided themes are : 1. Haunted house. 2.Vault break-in  .
9) *Tech Improv*: Tech Improv is a laughter-packed blend of tech-knowledge in Improv games to enable students to create a fun and interactive learning experience with mind engaging activities.
10) *Game Filler*: The events will be Beat the bar, racing simulator and guess my moves.
11) *TechTalks*: A Tech Influencer would appear as a guest speaker.

12) *Capture the motion*- There will be a 360 degree spinning camera in the middle of the hall, participants will come and use that camera to make a reel and post it on the given hashtag #capturethemotion and #personafest2023.
13) *Cyber Shenanigans*: Ethical live hacking demonstration to participants.
